[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7668,
        "end_time": 11309,
        "text": "Depression is the leading cause\nof disability in the world."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11309,
        "end_time": 12382,
        "text": "In the United States,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12382,
        "end_time": 15683,
        "text": "close to 10% of adults \nstruggle with depression."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 15683,
        "end_time": 17358,
        "text": "But because it&#39;s a mental illness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17358,
        "end_time": 21598,
        "text": "it can be a lot harder to understand\nthan, say, high cholesterol."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 21598,
        "end_time": 25390,
        "text": "One major source of confusion is\nthe difference between having depression"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 25390,
        "end_time": 27963,
        "text": "and just feeling depressed."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 27963,
        "end_time": 31492,
        "text": "Almost everyone feels down\nfrom time to time."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 31492,
        "end_time": 32711,
        "text": "Getting a bad grade,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 32711,
        "end_time": 33808,
        "text": "losing a job,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 33808,
        "end_time": 34831,
        "text": "having an argument,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 34831,
        "end_time": 38064,
        "text": "even a rainy day can bring on\nfeelings of sadness."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 38064,
        "end_time": 39891,
        "text": "Sometimes there&#39;s no trigger at all."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 39891,
        "end_time": 42006,
        "text": "It just pops up out of the blue."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 42006,
        "end_time": 43549,
        "text": "Then circumstances change,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 43549,
        "end_time": 46206,
        "text": "and those sad feelings disappear."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 46206,
        "end_time": 48419,
        "text": "Clinical depression is different."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 48419,
        "end_time": 49896,
        "text": "It&#39;s a medical disorder,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 49896,
        "end_time": 52778,
        "text": "and it won&#39;t go away \njust because you want it to."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 52778,
        "end_time": 55180,
        "text": "It lingers for at least \ntwo consecutive weeks,"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 55180,
        "end_time": 58783,
        "text": "and significantly interferes \nwith one&#39;s ability to work,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 58783,
        "end_time": 59590,
        "text": "play,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 59590,
        "end_time": 60996,
        "text": "or love."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 60996,
        "end_time": 63277,
        "text": "Depression can have a lot\nof different symptoms:"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 63277,
        "end_time": 64281,
        "text": "a low mood,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 64281,
        "end_time": 66912,
        "text": "loss of interest in things\nyou&#39;d normally enjoy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 66912,
        "end_time": 68485,
        "text": "changes in appetite,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 68485,
        "end_time": 70835,
        "text": "feeling worthless or excessively guilty,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 70835,
        "end_time": 73531,
        "text": "sleeping either too much or too little,"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 73531,
        "end_time": 75363,
        "text": "poor concentration,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 75363,
        "end_time": 77198,
        "text": "restlessness or slowness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 77198,
        "end_time": 78681,
        "text": "loss of energy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 78681,
        "end_time": 81215,
        "text": "or recurrent thoughts of suicide."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 81215,
        "end_time": 83461,
        "text": "If you have at least five\nof those symptoms,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 83461,
        "end_time": 85445,
        "text": "according to psychiatric guidelines,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 85445,
        "end_time": 88924,
        "text": "you qualify for a diagnosis of depression."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 88924,
        "end_time": 91292,
        "text": "And it&#39;s not just behavioral symptoms."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 91292,
        "end_time": 95406,
        "text": "Depression has physical manifestations\ninside the brain."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 95406,
        "end_time": 96511,
        "text": "First of all,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 96511,
        "end_time": 99092,
        "text": "there are changes that could be seen\nwith the naked eye"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 99092,
        "end_time": 100510,
        "text": "and X-ray vision."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 100510,
        "end_time": 104783,
        "text": "These include smaller frontal lobes\nand hippocampal volumes."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 104783,
        "end_time": 106871,
        "text": "On a more microscale,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 106871,
        "end_time": 109351,
        "text": "depression is associated \nwith a few things:"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 109351,
        "end_time": 113241,
        "text": "the abnormal transmission or depletion\nof certain neurotransmitters,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 113241,
        "end_time": 116870,
        "text": "especially serotonin, norepinephrine,\nand dopamine,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 116870,
        "end_time": 118628,
        "text": "blunted circadian rhythms,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 118628,
        "end_time": 123338,
        "text": "or specific changes in the REM\nand slow-wave parts of your sleep cycle,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 123338,
        "end_time": 125303,
        "text": "and hormone abnormalities,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 125303,
        "end_time": 130187,
        "text": "such as high cortisol and deregulation\nof thyroid hormones."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 130187,
        "end_time": 132950,
        "text": "But neuroscientists still don&#39;t have\na complete picture"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 132950,
        "end_time": 135101,
        "text": "of what causes depression."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 135101,
        "end_time": 140075,
        "text": "It seems to have to do with a complex\ninteraction between genes and environment,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 140075,
        "end_time": 141839,
        "text": "but we don&#39;t have a diagnostic tool"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 141839,
        "end_time": 146112,
        "text": "that can accurately predict where\nor when it will show up."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 146112,
        "end_time": 148619,
        "text": "And because depression symptoms\nare intangible,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 148619,
        "end_time": 152467,
        "text": "it&#39;s hard to know who might look fine\nbut is actually struggling."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 152467,
        "end_time": 154954,
        "text": "According to the National Institute\nof Mental Health,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 154954,
        "end_time": 157847,
        "text": "it takes the average person\nsuffering with a mental illness"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 157847,
        "end_time": 161138,
        "text": "over ten years to ask for help."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 161138,
        "end_time": 163115,
        "text": "But there are very effective treatments."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 163115,
        "end_time": 167611,
        "text": "Medications and therapy complement\neach other to boost brain chemicals."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 167611,
        "end_time": 170631,
        "text": "In extreme cases,\nelectroconvulsive therapy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 170631,
        "end_time": 173553,
        "text": "which is like a controlled seizure\nin the patient&#39;s brain,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 173553,
        "end_time": 175668,
        "text": "is also very helpful."
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 175668,
        "end_time": 176989,
        "text": "Other promising treatments,"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 176989,
        "end_time": 179621,
        "text": "like transcranial magnetic stimulation,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 179621,
        "end_time": 181799,
        "text": "are being investigated, too."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 181799,
        "end_time": 184405,
        "text": "So, if you know someone \nstruggling with depression,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 184405,
        "end_time": 188777,
        "text": "encourage them, gently, to seek out\nsome of these options."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 188777,
        "end_time": 191176,
        "text": "You might even offer to help\nwith specific tasks,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 191176,
        "end_time": 193291,
        "text": "like looking up therapists in the area,"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 193291,
        "end_time": 196026,
        "text": "or making a list of questions\nto ask a doctor."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 196026,
        "end_time": 197689,
        "text": "To someone with depression,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 197689,
        "end_time": 200741,
        "text": "these first steps can seem insurmountable."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 200741,
        "end_time": 203026,
        "text": "If they feel guilty or ashamed,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 203026,
        "end_time": 205590,
        "text": "point out that depression \nis a medical condition,"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 205590,
        "end_time": 207641,
        "text": "just like asthma or diabetes."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 207641,
        "end_time": 210274,
        "text": "It&#39;s not a weakness \nor a personality trait,"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 210274,
        "end_time": 213516,
        "text": "and they shouldn&#39;t expect themselves\nto just get over it"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 213516,
        "end_time": 216866,
        "text": "anymore than they could will themselves\nto get over a broken arm."
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 216866,
        "end_time": 219461,
        "text": "If you haven&#39;t experienced \ndepression yourself,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 219461,
        "end_time": 222804,
        "text": "avoid comparing it to times\nyou&#39;ve felt down."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 222804,
        "end_time": 226977,
        "text": "Comparing what they&#39;re experiencing\nto normal, temporary feelings of sadness"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 226977,
        "end_time": 229599,
        "text": "can make them feel guilty for struggling."
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 229599,
        "end_time": 232936,
        "text": "Even just talking about \ndepression openly can help."
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 232936,
        "end_time": 237315,
        "text": "For example, research shows that asking\nsomeone about suicidal thoughts"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 237315,
        "end_time": 239814,
        "text": "actually reduces their suicide risk."
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 239814,
        "end_time": 243766,
        "text": "Open conversations about mental illness\nhelp erode stigma"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 243766,
        "end_time": 246502,
        "text": "and make it easier \nfor people to ask for help."
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 246502,
        "end_time": 248293,
        "text": "And the more patients seek treatment,"
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 248293,
        "end_time": 250992,
        "text": "the more scientists will learn\nabout depression,"
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 250992,
        "end_time": 253209,
        "text": "and the better the treatments will get."
    }
]